<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>문의 작성</title>

    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
            background-color: #F5F7FA;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="text-gray-800">

{{> studentLayout/studentHeader }}

<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 py-10">

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-gray-100 p-8 space-y-6">

        <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-pen-to-square text-blue-600"></i>
            강의 문의 작성
        </h1>

        <form method="post" action="/courseQuestionWrite" class="space-y-6">

            <input type="hidden" name="courseNo" value="{{courseNo}}"/>

            <!-- 제목 -->
            <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">제목</label>
                <input type="text" name="courseQuestionTitle" required
                       class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 text-sm p-3
                              focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500" />
            </div>

            <!-- 내용 -->
            <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">내용</label>
                <textarea name="courseQuestionContent" rows="6" required
                          class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 text-sm p-3
                                 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"></textarea>
            </div>

            <!-- 공개 / 비밀글 선택 -->
            <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">공개 설정</label>

                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-6 text-sm">

                    <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                        <input type="radio" name="privatePost" value="0" checked
                               class="text-blue-600 border-gray-300">
                        <span class="text-gray-700">공개</span>
                    </label>

                    <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                        <input type="radio" name="privatePost" value="1"
                               class="text-blue-600 border-gray-300">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-lock text-xs"></i>
                        <span class="text-gray-700">비밀글</span>
                    </label>
                </div>

                <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">
                    비밀글은 작성자와 담당 교수만 볼 수 있어요.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- 버튼 -->
            <div class="flex justify-end gap-3">
                <a href="/courseQuestionList?courseNo={{courseNo}}"
                   class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 text-sm text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50">
                    목록
                </a>
                <button type="submit"
                        class="px-5 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-medium
                               hover:bg-blue-700">
                    등록하기
                </button>
            </div>
        </form>

    </div>
</main>

</body>
</html>
